title: Episode 74 "The Interim" w/ Memphis Bleek
itunes:title: Episode 74 "The Interim" w/ Memphis Bleek
description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode the guys, joined by Memphis Bleek, talk Charlie Murphy, mumble rap, Kendrick Lamar, Roc-a-Fella records, EFN's "Coming Home' documentary series, and a lot more! Drink Champs would like to send their heart felt condolences to the Murphy family. Rest In Peace Charlie Murphy. --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
